Investor support













 

Investor support
We provide dedicated support to our investors and distribution partners with the latest investment research, in-depth analysis of the local and global markets, and up-to-date product information.

Support for individual investors
1. Investment account information 

Please contact the intermediary who sets up the investment account and handles your investment instruction on account details.

2. Investment updates 

Read our latest views on major markets and the most up-to-date insights from our investment professionals


3. Fund-related information 

View our latest fund prices and fund performance


4. Others 

View the answers to the frequently asked questions
Call our Customer Services Hotline on 852 2284 1118 (Monday to Friday, 9 am - 5.30 pm)

Support for intermediaries

View our latest fund prices and fund performance

View the answers to the frequently asked questions
Call our Customer Services Hotline on 852 2284 1118 (Monday to Friday, 9 am - 5.30 pm)













