Hong Kong

Retirement investments

MPF
Members choice
Market insights
Education centre
Contact us















We are one of the largest retirement fund managers in Hong Kong and we have been managing retirement assets for Hong Kong clients since 1973. We have an established track record in managing pension assets for our clients, Members Choice and MPF scheme members. We are committed to the Hong Kong retirement funds business and aim to be best in class for the MPF-related services that we provide.



MPF
Mandatory retirement schemes for Hong Kong employees.

More





Members Choice
Retirement schemes with fund choices for employees.

More















Members Choice

Retirement schemes with fund choices for employees.
