											Hong Kong, 
										
											Japan, 
										
											North America, 
										
											Southeast Asia, 
										
											Taiwan, 
										
											Western Europe
										
									







Product/Service Range:


										
											Stock Broking / Dealing & Related Services, 
										
											Asset Management
										
									







China Experience:

HSBC Global Asset Management has established a joint venture with Shanxi Trust and Investment Corporation Limited, namely HSBC Jintrust Fund Management Company Limited, since November 2005. We have successfully tapped into the domestic fund management market by offering a variety of lifecycle, equity and bond funds. HSBC Jintrust has funds under management of RMB10.087 billion as at the end of June 2011.







