Career opportunities
There is a wealth of opportunity at HSBC Global Asset management. Our long term success depends on our ability to attract and retain talented professionals from the marketplace.

One of our greatest strengths lies in our diversity and this is true for the whole of the HSBC Group. Our local roots and local presence enable us to meet the needs of our clients who can trust in the HSBC Group's global strength.

The business comprises a wide range of activities, in locations around the globe. Please take some time to see if we have the right opportunity for you.

Internship programme
                  At HSBC Global Asset Management, we run a summer internship programme, open to penultimate year students.

Analyst programme
                  At HSBC Global Asset Management, we run two career streams for graduates.

How to apply
                  Apply for our graduate programmes or learn more about career opportunities with HSBC Global Asset Management and the wider HSBC group.














