                    Why HSBC?
                







We offer an inclusive, values-led culture, tailored learning and development programmes and competitive benefits.





                    Meet our people
                







What is it like to work for HSBC? Employees from across the bank discuss their experiences.





                    Explore our business
                







We have roles in retail, commercial, investment and private banking and a range of operational and functional teams.











                    Key hiring areas
                







We recruit for a broad range of roles worldwide, as well as having some key hiring areas to support business needs. Find out about our current recruitment priorities. 







                    Where we hire
                







Discover the locations where we offer exciting career opportunities.





                    Careers events
                







Find out more about careers at HSBC by attending one of our events.









                    Students and graduates 
                









Whether you are a school leaver, a university student or graduate, we have placements, programmes and entry-level positions to suit you.




