HSBC MPF - HSBC Hong Kong 
























The world's local bank















    Financial market is ever-changing. Keeping abreast of up-to-date market trends and information helps you make more informed investment decisions and capture the most of investment opportunities.
  

2017 Global Multi-asset Market Outlook
Walt Lau
Product Specialist, Multi-asset and WealthHSBC Global Asset Management (Hong Kong) Limited








Video Duration:
4:53


Release Date:
May 2017


Language:
Cantonese(with English subtitle)













Key highlights:
•Risk appetite in the market began to resume with global equities rising. For the time being, the global economic activity continues to look strong.
•As of end of March 2017, the MPF mixed asset funds maintained less exposure in government bonds and shorter bond duration.
•Understanding their own risk tolerance level is essential for MPF members before they consider the investments that match their risk appetite.
•Mixed asset funds offer a suite of risk levels through different weighting in equities and bonds. Fund managers allocate assets according to the investment environment and thus relieve the burden of members.


Risk disclosure and disclaimers
This video is not intended to provide investment advice and does not constitute a recommendation or advice to any prospective customers. Readers should not act on any information in the video without seeking specific professional advice.
